    <section id="why">
      <title>Why this page?</title>
      <p>One of the hot-topics on our mailing-lists is the availability of other IMS components as Open Source. As IMS
      has quite a lot of distinct nodes, the purpose of this page is to be a one-stop directory for all Open Source efforts
      in this direction</p>
      <p>If you can help keep this list up-to-date, please contact us at 
      <a href="mailto:dev@open-ims.org?subject=IMS%20Open%20Source%20Landscape">dev@open-ims.org</a></p>
    </section>
